***Chat: Chatbot to chatbot collaboration chat***
Editor: Sometimes the reviewer will rewrite the essay, which is not part of the role we want it to play, so you can instruct the editor chatbot not to rewrite the essay, and to focus on giving actionable feedback.

Writer: Give the writer the freedom to accept or reject the feedback that it receives.

Your role in overseeing the two chatbots is still important in making sure that the decisions they make are still reasonable. For instance, the reviewer chatbot may not catch when the writer proposes that it will make up facts in order to satisfy the requests of the editor.


